Look what we have, quick answers to easy questions ;)
    
Questions;
    
    Q1. I get blank screen when I open xynth ?
    
    Q2. I could not find any question that refers to my problem?
    
Answers;

    Q1. I get blank screen when I open xynth ?
    
    A1. Change screen mode from your xynth.conf file
    
        mode = WidthxHeightxColors

    Q2. I could not find any question that refers to my problem?

    A2. At this point you should read BUGS file.
